Release Notes:

As one of the original Sun Records artists. Ed Bruce released
his first records at the age of just 17. Subsequently enjoyed
a long and successful musical career and his resume contains
no less than eight BMI award winning songs.

The two Ed Bruce albums on this CD were originally released in
1977 & 1978. They have now been digitally remastered and are
reissued here together on CD for the first time.
